    {
      "id": "PopularPost17609",
      "post_content": "Pretty sure that trick doesn't work anymore, Twigster. Damage isn't used on the stack whether it's first strike or not. You're only allowed to use spells and abilities during the Declare Attackers, Declare Blockers and after the Combat Phase. So this is still useful if you use it after they declare a blocker that could kill your attacker if they deal damage at the same time, but otherwise it can't be used to do stop an attacker's damage completely.",
      "posted_by": "CeremonialBathory",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost17609\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">Pretty sure that trick doesn't work anymore, Twigster. Damage isn't used on the stack whether it's first strike or not. You're only allowed to use spells and abilities during the Declare Attackers, Declare Blockers and after the Combat Phase. So this is still useful if you use it after they declare a blocker that could kill your attacker if they deal damage at the same time, but otherwise it can't be used to do stop an attacker's damage completely.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '17609'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2558\">CeremonialBathory</span>\r\n                                (8/12/2009 1:58:58 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\